{"tid":205830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【象鱷大戰】象仔飲水遇鱷撲出咬鼻 象群齊心幫佢逃出生天","createTime":"2017-04-18T05:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T08:11:16.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b102d8b14b3e0310d893183566455b51e67198","tid":205830,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170417/large/1492421482_2f0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170417%2Flarge%2F1492421482_2f0a.jpg&h=505f4d1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鱷魚，一向是出色的獵人，經常埋伏在意想不到的地方，靜候獵物到來。非洲馬拉維（Malawi）一隻小象到河邊飲水，便被潛伏在水中的鱷魚突襲咬著象鼻，小象與鱷魚「隻揪」，最終在其他大象幫忙下，逃出生天不致成為鱷魚大餐。<br />\n<br />\n現居英國的科學家生物醫學家馬卡加（Alexander Makanga），本月初在利翁代國家公園（Liwonde National Park）目睹整個過程。當時一群大象到河邊喝水，一隻小象可能很口渴，一馬當先衝到河邊。但一隻鱷魚突然從水中撲出，咬著小象的象鼻不放，小象立即團團轉，企圖擺脫鱷魚的緊咬。<br />\n其他象雖然緊張，初時卻瑟縮一旁不敢施以援手，只旁觀小象獨力奮戰。其後一隻大象終於上前幫忙，令小象脫困。"},{"pid":"d61c4df5262d2c2ce7eba3af95f301638a23a1e2","tid":205830,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:27:54.000Z","msg":"大象一腳踢撚死隻鱷魚"},{"pid":"19c354a352ea0d3af0ebe993455f74d9e36e39ef","tid":205830,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:28:04.000Z","msg":"如果我屋企好大，會想養返隻象<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa21ad19025c204c1ceea74c11e43db5aa9f65e","tid":205830,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:29:25.000Z","msg":"大鱷捉象仔去返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8462f4e534f9976112588daf13df76aaefb6c9d3","tid":205830,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T05:31:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大鱷捉象仔去返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n象仔:又要番工啦啦啦啦啦啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/18/133122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F18%2F133122_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6bee4ce8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"feda0802149ae4dd304e93811ece25fd37404ca1","tid":205830,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T06:01:17.000Z","msg":"link 呢屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2702a85710dd4f9abf2c4a918ee39ea01756ea99","tid":205830,"uid":44333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:08:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大象一腳踢撚死隻鱷魚</blockquote><br />\n積下口德啦"},{"pid":"f2d1eba42ce61e63c29f12080cb3be1276a9e4b7","tid":205830,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"枝飲管穿左窿以後吸水係咪要大力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be04545ef68d136b4cd403f661108cffbc82479","tid":205830,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"有無link 睇  ?"}]}